lead_paragraph: Spain started their World Cup qualifying campaign with a crushing 8-0 win over Liechtenstein, laying down a marker in Group G with a ruthless second-half display on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Ruthless Spain Maul Liechtenstein to Lay Down Marker
